private final AtomicInteger ctl = new AtomicInteger(ctlOf(RUNNING, 0));
private static final int COUNT_BITS = Integer.SIZE - 3;
private static final int CAPACITY   = (1 << COUNT_BITS) - 1;

private static final int RUNNING    = -1 << COUNT_BITS;
private static final int SHUTDOWN   =  0 << COUNT_BITS;
private static final int STOP       =  1 << COUNT_BITS;
private static final int TIDYING    =  2 << COUNT_BITS;
private static final int TERMINATED =  3 << COUNT_BITS;
```

> COUNT_BITS  29(32-3)29
> CAPACITY = 2^29-1=536870911  
> RUNNING  111 00000000000000000000000000000 
> SHUTDOWN  000 00000000000000000000000000000 
> STOP  001 00000000000000000000000000000 
> TIDYING  010 00000000000000000000000000000 , TIDYING  terminated()
> TERMINATED  011 00000000000000000000000000000 terminated() 

- RUNNING -> SHUTDOWN shutdown() 
- (RUNNING or SHUTDOWN) -> STOP shutdownNow()  shutDown()  shutDownNow() 
- SHUTDOWN -> TIDYING SHUTDOWN  TIDYING
- STOP -> TIDYING
- TIDYING -> TERMINATED terminated() 

